com.microsoft.windowsazure.services.queue.models

Class GetQueueMetadataResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.windowsazure.services.queue.models.GetQueueMetadataResult

  • public class GetQueueMetadataResult
extends java.lang.Object
    A wrapper class for the result returned from a Queue Service REST API operation to get queue metadata. This is returned by calls to implementations of QueueContract.getQueueMetadata(String) and QueueContract.getQueueMetadata(String, QueueServiceOptions).

    See the Get Queue Metadata documentation on MSDN for details of the underlying Queue Service REST API operation.

      • getMetadata

        public java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> getMetadata()
        Gets the metadata collection of key-value String pairs currently set on a queue. Queue metadata is a user-defined collection of key-value pairs that is opaque to the server.
        Returns:
        A HashMap of key-value String pairs containing the metadata set on the queue.
